OL,5, Crypto companies must offer customers a
OL,6, 24-hour "cooling-off period" in        
OL,7, sweeping changes to how the digital    
OL,8, assets can be marketed in the UK.      
OL,10,FNew investors will have to wait a full 
OL,11,Fday before they can complete their     
OL,12,Ftransaction.                           
OL,14,FThe government estimates up to one out 
OL,15,Fof every 10 of UK adults now owns some 
OL,16,Fform of crypto.                        
OL,18,FBosses of companies that fail to comply
OL,19,Fcould face up to two years'            
OL,20,Fimprisonment, a fine, or both.         
